IMPORTANT NOTICE: APRIL 17, 2020 


This afternoon Governor Pritzker extended the school closure mandate for the remainder of the school year because of COVID-19. This news is sad for our students, our staff and the entire school community. I would have never imagined this is how we would end the 2019-2020 school year and I am disappointed. I miss seeing our students in classrooms, hallways, and on our athletic fields every day. There are many questions you will have and, honestly, I have many questions too. As an administration we have many details to figure out in the coming days so we can communicate with you all. READ MORE...... 


















