2020 SIX FLAGS GRAD NITE - Updated 4-1-20 


Due to the extension of the COVID-19 Social Distancing Guidelines we are canceling the Grad-Nite 2020 trip on May 16, 2020. There are two option for any students who have purchased grad nite tickets such as: 


Converting your tickets to “any day” tickets that you can use through the end of the 2020 season. 


Voiding the agreement and refund your payments. 



If you have purchased tickets ahead of time, please email Dr Toulios 
, Mrs. Dergance 
, or Mrs. Whittinghill 

















